@host = http://localhost:8080

### ✅ List without parameters (page 0, size 10)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/user-types

### ✅ List with pagination (page=0&size=5)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/user-types
    ?page=0
    &size=5

### ✅ List with ASC sorting by name
GET {{host}}/api/v1/user-types
    ?sort=name
    &direction=ASC

### ✅ List with DESC sorting by name
GET {{host}}/api/v1/user-types
    ?sort=name
    &direction=DESC

### ✅ Filter by existing name
GET {{host}}/api/v1/user-types
    ?filter=name
    &filterValue=Owner

### ✅ Filter by non-existent name (returns empty list)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/user-types
    ?filter=name
    &filterValue=Driver

### ❌ Filter by invalid field (400 Bad Request)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/user-types
    ?filter=nome
    &filterValue=Owner
